{"tid":1334180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問搞臨時議會可以點樣be water？","createTime":"2019-07-20T04:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:01:31.000Z","uid":122994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"716dd1cb42fd919a9ee9aa59f014514131a6ce8b","tid":1334180,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拿，屌你老母，港獨好明顯係長遠唯一選項黎既，臨時議會同臨時政府點都要搞，係差在幾時。<br />\n<br />\n但我見D人攞衝立會同搞臨立會比，話咩衝之前都無人知會work，唔搞點知有無人支持。<br />\n<br />\n但淨係一點都好唔同啦，衝立會一入到就立桿見影，入完可以be water走。搞臨立會點be water？唔講咩認受性合法性，我地起碼要長期keep到個議會，搞個零月出兩三個議案先叫一回事啦，唔係外媒只會當係小學雞中二病，仲妨礙左我地日後搞議會道氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外搞臨立會D議員又要出樣又要出名，到時黑警拉人封艇，泛民又冷處理，又犧牲義士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以一句講曬，政府係要搞，議會都係要搞，最好唔係臨時添，但依家搞同今次be water社運既綱領有D格格不入。各位巴打三思。"},{"pid":"e84c2f998783b1ac7614f4c0e709d56a0e2cfea3","tid":1334180,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"721 721<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUEVzN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUEVzN9.jpg&h=b7c1c75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7eeQmv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7eeQmv.jpg&h=a65e5982&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d49cf1da76bb7a56f388bcf54e80cbae1639153","tid":1334180,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b874b473b652a2f76c6d44edabe7cb97b83d1f62","tid":1334180,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9031110476784b394831b7a0a82361609aa5dc38","tid":1334180,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img 